Moreover, the invoices issued by the Együtt Foundation and Harmadik Évezredért and the association XXI. Szazadi Kulturális Egyesület and Biztos Pont have also been falsely leaked due to formal deviations - not matching the format of the invoice and the incorrect stamp.
As in the case of Ravenna k. s. or Sport Camp in Kunfehértó, whose representatives denied that they would issue invoices.
For example, the forgers did not notice that HIB s. r. o. of Nyíregyháza was in liquidation at the time of 2001 when a group from the Fiatal Városért Society was eating there, which is why, according to our information, the liquidation commissioner of the company also denied that he had published the paper.
The invoices were exhibited consciously
